title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown at the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: When exporting data in two tables where one is placed inside a grid cell, the expected result is that the data are exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell. 3. Attempt to export the data.
